Text.string: If you're hearin' this, the job is yours. I don't care who ya are. I just need someone to take my jackass of a pappy on a drive-'round for the errands. But mostly just ta get him outta my hair for a minute. Come on by my place and pick him up.
You here fer the job? Good. It's about damn time somebody came by for it. Well, the jackass is in the car over there—go ahead and take him 'round till he quits yappin'.
Now take me down roundabout there and kill some damn spiderants for me. And be quick about it, you festering wart juice!
See, I make me a suppository outta them milk pods. Helps keep me regular. You DO want me to be regular, don'tcha?!
Could you kill 'em any slower, you wet hemorrhoid? I ain't gettin' any younger.
Hmph. Took ya long enough, piss-breath. I got shit-elves earnin' time-and-a-half buildin' log cabins in my colon. Could use a mudslide to put 'em outta business!
Y'know, it's funny that you ain't got nothin' better to do than drive my old ass around. You must have less friends than a syphilitic varkid.
Now I'm meeting up with a trader to make a deal on his prized coin collection. What the hell are ya waiting for?!
Heh heh heh! Looks like the bandits got him. Which means I don't have to pay for the coins! All right, new plan, you taint-licker. Head into that bandit camp and get that coin collection!
What's taking so long? Can't you even waste a few bandits, you pus-sucker?!
Ha! Yes! Now bring them coins on back to Pappy, and we'll get a move on. And hurry up, grundle-sweat! Ain't got all day.
You just do whatever I say, don'tcha? Heh heh. Why, you're like a fancy prostitute of killin' things and takin' things. You're pathetic.
You ungrateful little... Why, I oughta tan yer hide just like when you was a youngin'. You were a mistake then, and you're still a mistake now!
All right, dimwit. I've been staring at your ugly-mug for too long. Take me somewhere pretty!
Now shut yer trap and sit quiet!
Well, what're you still lookin' at me for? You tryna make out with me or something? Get me outta here already. And NOW! I got one more errand to run.
That's right. Do whatever Pappy says. Heh-heh-heh-heh...
This sonuvabitch dentist stole my good dentures and I want 'em back! Said he wanted extra teeth for his teeth or some bandit nonsense. Get me them teeth!
Knock on the damn door already and get that sonuvabitch out here!
Whadda you want?!
Pappy needs his dentures.
Apparently Pappy needs dentures.
The old one requires false teeth.
That yapping old coot says you got his dentures.
I don't know what the flaming crap you're talking about.
No, HIS teeth! Take HIS teeth, you maggot-infested foreskin!
Yeah?! Whatever you say, you rotten old bastard!||Bring him back after his errands. Or don't. Might be doin' me a favor.
Nobody's taking MY teeth!
Pick up them teeth! I needs 'em! When I say pick it up, you pick it up! Jump through the hoop, dog!
Now get over here and take me home. I said NOW!
Don't expect me to get all sappy and go off thankin' you or nothing. Just take me home, you shit-dipped tortilla chip.
You friggin' ass-backward lunatic! Cut it out, right this instant!
Are you kidding me with this?! You dumpster-fire of a burnin' asshole!
We ain't supposed to be up this high! What the hell's wrong with you, you crusty chode?!
You nearly took my head off with that stunt, you slack-jawed spitwad!
You incompetent jerkoff!
Do that again and I'ma give you a knuckle sandwich!
You trying to kill me, you damp piss-stain?
Stop doing that, you bloody skidmark!
What do you think you're doing, you skunky bunghole?
Would you slow down already?! This ain't some kinda death race!
Slow the hell down, you bucket of syphilitic piss!
Don't make me take that wheel away from ya... friggin' pus-rag!
Now get outta my car, you truckin' idjit. Hey, Lizzie! Give 'em all that money I keep beneath the mattress!
Oh, good. He's back in one piece. Hoo. Ray. Thanks for getting him outta here for a bit. Even if it was only a few minutes of peace and quiet, it was... blissful. Here's Pappy's cash stash for ya.

I don't know who you are, but you're clearly a turd taco in a stank-ass tortilla. Who needs you?! Not me, that's for damn sure! Now get to drivin'! And don't drive like a maniac! Y'hear me, ya walkin' pit stain?
You'll never know where the gold's buried!
I'll keep hatin' you from hell!
Aww, piss on you, prick!
Huh... so he's, uh... he's dead then, is he? Oh, no. How tragic. Why? He was taken before his time. Woe is me.||Come on back, though. I still wanna thank ya for, uh... helpin' me out.

It just so happens I finally received my inheritance thanks to you. I'm sure my father's tragic untimely death was a complete accident, so I should still thank you for tryin' to take him 'round on those errands, so thanks! Bye now!
Now get to killin', you useless crap-factory!
Now git out there before I go upside your empty friggin' head! I can smell that sniveling, coin-tradin' pile of crotch rot from a mile away! Go find 'em!
Oh, you're just terrific.
Keep talkin' like that, old man. See where it gets you.
You are most unpleasant.
Ahhh, keep on yer yappin', pappy. I'll do you what for.
Like I care what you think! Now I bet Lizzie would be happier'n a skag in scat if I never came back at all. But if you keep me alive, I'll make sure you get yer money!
